name: Noce di Ajilenakh
desc: A fruit that grows on evergreen trees within desert oases. The flesh under the tough skin is thick, sweet, and delicious, making it an important food source amongst the desert peoples.

value.text: Found in the desert oases of Sumeru

desc.text:
Message
"I heard many bandits have been popping up in the desert, and many merchants are refusing to travel the routes there. The price of Ajilenakh Nuts might start to skyrocket."
Another Person's Message
"Awesome! I'm selling all my mushrooms for Ajilenakh Nuts right now! Haha! Perhaps this is the courage and vision of the Alkindi Clan!"
Acting Manager's Reply
I'd love to see your wealth multiply, but I'd like to state that my shop is not responsible for any losses that may arise from the information on this board.
